name: TD Q U.S. Small-Mid-Cap Equity ETF
longDescription: In seeking to achieve this objective, by investing primarily in, or gaining exposure to, equity securities of small or medium-sized issuers located in the United States. In seeking to achieve this objective, the Fund uses a quantitative equity strategy to optimize exposure to a large number of securities, broadly diversified across all sectors, that are expected to outperform the overall market. A quantitative equity strategy is the selection of equity securities based on mathematical or rules-based algorithm. TD Q U.S. SmallMidCap Equity ETF seeks to achieve longterm capital growth.
